sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant API as Orchestrator API<br/>8033/TCP HTTP
    participant HealthSrv as Health Server<br/>8034/TCP HTTP
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as TGIS / Caikit NLP<br/>8033|8085/TCP gRPC
    participant OpenAI as OpenAI-compatible API<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant OTEL as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 1: Text Generation with Input/Output Detection (Unary)
    Client->>API: POST /api/v2/text/generation-detection<br/>TLS optional, Passthrough headers
    API->>OTEL: Trace span: request received
    API->>Chunker: Chunk input text<br/>gRPC, mTLS optional, Bearer optional
    Chunker-->>API: Chunked tokens
    API->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (input detection)<br/>HTTP, TLS optional, Bearer optional
    Detector-->>API: Detection results (scores)
    Note over API: Check input scores vs thresholds<br/>Block if harmful content detected
    API->>TGIS: Generate text (unary)<br/>gRPC, mTLS optional, Bearer optional
    TGIS-->>API: Generated text
    API->>Chunker: Chunk output text<br/>gRPC, mTLS optional
    Chunker-->>API: Chunked tokens
    API->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/generation (output detection)<br/>HTTP, TLS optional
    Detector-->>API: Detection results (scores)
    Note over API: Check output scores vs thresholds<br/>Filter if harmful content detected
    API-->>Client: Generation response<br/>(with detection metadata)
    API->>OTEL: Trace span: request complete

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 2: Chat Completions with Detection (Streaming)
    Client->>API: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>TLS optional, Passthrough headers
    API->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (input - text_contents)<br/>HTTP, TLS optional
    Detector-->>API: Input content detection results
    API->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/chat (input - text_chat)<br/>HTTP, TLS optional
    Detector-->>API: Input chat detection results
    Note over API: Check input scores vs thresholds
    API->>OpenAI: POST /v1/chat/completions (streaming SSE)<br/>HTTP, TLS optional, Bearer optional
    loop Streaming chunks
        OpenAI-->>API: SSE chunk
        API->>Chunker: BidiStreaming chunk<br/>gRPC bidi-stream, mTLS optional
        Chunker-->>API: Tokenized chunk
        API->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents (output detection)<br/>HTTP, TLS optional
        Detector-->>API: Chunk detection results
        Note over API: DetectionBatchStream coordinates<br/>ordered batch release
        API-->>Client: SSE chunk (filtered)
    end
    API-->>Client: Stream complete

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 3: Standalone Content Detection
    Client->>API: POST /api/v2/text/detection/content<br/>TLS optional, Passthrough headers
    API->>Chunker: Chunk input text<br/>gRPC, mTLS optional
    Chunker-->>API: Chunked tokens
    API->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>HTTP, TLS optional (parallel detectors)
    Detector-->>API: Detection results
    API-->>Client: Detection response

    Note over Client,OTEL: Health Check Flow
    Client->>HealthSrv: GET /health (liveness)
    HealthSrv-->>Client: 200 OK (name + version)
    Client->>HealthSrv: GET /info (readiness)
    HealthSrv->>TGIS: Health probe (gRPC/HTTP)
    HealthSrv->>Chunker: Health probe (gRPC)
    HealthSrv->>Detector: GET /health (HTTP/8081)
    HealthSrv->>OpenAI: GET /health (HTTP)
    TGIS-->>HealthSrv: Status
    Chunker-->>HealthSrv: Status
    Detector-->>HealthSrv: Status
    OpenAI-->>HealthSrv: Status
    HealthSrv-->>Client: 200 OK (aggregated health)
